Live from Milwaukee, ventriloquist Jeff Dunham and his collection of colorful
puppet characters -- affectionately known as the "suitcase posse" -- delight 
sold-out crowds with this unique Christmas special from the stages of the Pabst 
Theater. Loaded with extras, this release features behind-the-scenes footage, 
outtakes, the uproarious "Ask Santa-Walter" skit and the side-splittling 
music video "Christmas Roadkill."
